                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"guidance-on-the-operation-of-aspa\"\u003eGuidance on the operation of ASPA\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/the-operation-of-the-animals-scientific-procedures-act-1986\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eGuidance on the operation of ASPA\u003c/a\u003e  explains how the act is administered and enforced and provides detailed guidance to licence holders and applicants.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"guidance-on-training\"\u003eGuidance on training\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/training-and-development-under-the-animals-scientific-procedures-act\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eGuidance on training and continuous professional development (CPD) under ASPA\u003c/a\u003e explains the governance framework and training requirements for licensing under ASPA. This replaces section 9 of the ‘Guidance on the operation of ASPA’.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"business-continuity-planning-guidance\"\u003eBusiness continuity planning guidance\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe \u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\"\u003e\n  \u003ca class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5e67b1a7d3bf7f2697cd91ef/ASRU_Guidance_on_BC_Managment_200304.pdf\"\u003ebusiness continuity planning guidance for establishments\u003c/a\u003e  (\u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"\u003e\u003cabbr title=\"Portable Document Format\" class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__abbr\"\u003ePDF\u003c/abbr\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"\u003e185 KB\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"\u003e13 pages\u003c/span\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e reminds and provides advice to establishment licence holders of the requirements for contingency planning, emergency response, and business continuity planning.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"technical-advice\"\u003eTechnical advice\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/animal-research-technical-advice\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003etechnical advice\u003c/a\u003e complements our guidance on the operation of the ASPA. The documents provide advice on interpretation of ASPA and are intended for licence holders and individuals working in this field and this includes:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ecode of practice for the care and accommodation of animals\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eadvice notes\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eadditional guidance documents\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you have any questions on these please contact: \u003ca href=\"mailto:ASRUBusiness@homeoffice.gov.uk\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eASRUBusiness@homeoffice.gov.uk\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e",
